{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \f1 modifier requiresGovernancePower(uint256 minPower) \{\line
    uint256 totalVotingPower = getTotalDecayedVotingPower();\line
    require(totalVotingPower >= minPower, "Governance power insufficient for this action");\line
    _;\line
\}\line
\line
// Examples:\line
function proposeParameterChange(...) requiresGovernancePower(1000e18) \{ ... \}\line
function proposeEmergencyPause(...) requiresGovernancePower(100e18) \{ ... \}\line
function proposeProtocolUpgrade(...) requiresGovernancePower(5000e18) \{ ... \}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 As total voting power decays below each threshold, that governance function becomes permanently uncallable.\par}
